    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Mint Condition Marvel \u2014 As Close to New as Used Gets!** Rarely does a used car come along in this kind of shape \u2014 and we mean it! This vehicle is in absolutely pristine, mint condition: flawless interior, spotless exterior, and everything running exactly as it should. No hidden surprises, no deferred maintenance \u2014 just a beautifully preserved car that's ready to impress from the moment you lay eyes on it. If you've been searching for a used car that feels like a fresh-off-the-lot experience, your search ends here. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will speak for itself! \ud83c\udf1f",
      "price": 46000.0,
