      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a dependable, well-cared-for car that represents solid value for the discerning used-car buyer. The exterior presents nicely, showing only minor surface imperfections consistent with normal everyday use, with no significant dents, rust, or damage to report. The interior is clean and functional, with moderate wear on high-contact areas like the seat bolsters and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been properly maintained, making it a trustworthy choice for daily driving. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and electronics \u2014 are in good working order. This is not a mint showroom piece, but it is a honest, road-ready vehicle that will serve its next owner well without requiring immediate repairs.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\u2728 Showroom Fresh & Absolutely Stunning \u2014 A True Mint Condition Treasure! This is the car you've been dreaming about \u2014 meticulously maintained and looking every bit as impressive as the day it was made! The exterior is spotless, with a gleaming finish free of scratches, dents, or blemishes. Step inside and you'll find an interior that's equally immaculate \u2014 clean, fresh, and beautifully preserved. Under the hood, everything is in top-notch working order, ready to deliver a smooth, confident ride from day one. If you want the very best without going brand new, this is your opportunity \u2014 don't let it pass you by! \ud83c\udf1f",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $16,500, a price that honestly reflects its fair condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. This car is functional and drivable, but it comes with visible signs of wear and age that you should expect at this price point. The exterior shows scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading consistent with years of regular use. The interior is serviceable but worn \u2014 expect faded upholstery, some scuffs on trim panels, and general cosmetic tiredness. Mechanically, the engine starts and runs, and the transmission shifts adequately, though we recommend a pre-purchase inspection by your own mechanic to identify any underlying issues we may not be fully aware of. Some minor mechanical attention may be needed in the near term. This is a practical, get-around vehicle for a buyer who understands they're purchasing a used car with history, not a showroom-ready ride. No major hidden surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly exceptional mint condition \u2014 an outstanding find for buyers who demand the very best. The car presents as virtually flawless, inside and out, with a spotless exterior finish free of scratches, dents, or blemishes, and an interior that looks and smells fresh with no wear, staining, or fading to be found. Mechanically, the vehicle performs at its absolute peak \u2014 the engine starts instantly, runs with silky smoothness, and delivers strong, responsive power. All systems, features, and electronics function perfectly, from climate control to infotainment to safety systems. This is a turn-key, worry-free purchase for a discerning buyer who wants a vehicle they can be proud of from day one, with no repairs, touch-ups, or maintenance surprises on the horizon.",
      "price": 46000.0,
